         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melb bot gard, 10/8/70. ¶  ¶ Can I not hope, reverend and dear Sir, to gain some essay from your unrivalled knowledge of Fungi for my Museum material You must by this time have got an enormous number ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.08.10</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Miles Berkeley</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Natural History Museum, London, Botany Library, Berkeley Correspondence, vol. 9.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melb bot gard, 10/8/70.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Can I not hope, reverend and dear Sir, to gain some essay from your unrivalled knowledge of Fungi for my Museum material You must by this time have got an enormous number of species of fungi from me from time to time, and you might at least do me a great service by naming any not requiring difficult or tedious investigation.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Species not easily determinable might be laid aside until a fairer opportunity for working on them may arise to you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Is the <name key="Xenodochus%20ligniperda">Xenodochus ligniperda</name> of Rabenhorst &amp; Willkomm transferred to another genus?<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Berkeley's note published with M to <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Gardeners' chronicle and agricultural gazette</seg>, December 1869 (in this edition as 69-12-00e). </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Xenodochus%20ligniperda">Xenodochus ligniperda</name>
            </p>
         </div>
